	* include/cdio/cdda.h, src/cd-paranoia/cd-paranoia.c: Remove a
	couple of unused SCSI fields.

2005-01-15 Saturday 16:05  Rocky Bernstein <rocky@panix.com>

	* include/cdio/cdda.h, lib/cdda_interface/Makefile.am,
