2004-07-26 Monday 03:58  Rocky Bernstein <rocky@panix.com>

	* include/cdio/scsi_mmc.h, lib/_cdio_linux.c, lib/scsi_mmc.c,
	lib/scsi_mmc_private.h: Try to make get_dvd_physical a common
