	src/cd-info.c: MIN_DRIVER, MIN_DEVICE_DRIVER, MAX_DEVICE_DRIVER ->
	CDIO_...  Add CDIO_MAX_DRIVER (distinct from CDIO_MAX_DEVICE_DRIVER
	
	cdio.c (cdio_open): was only scanning devices. Change to scan disk
	image files as well.

